title: Were not Ghana Make it
content:
BACKSTORY:
We started this leg in Third Place. During this leg we had to do boxing, carry wheelbarrows 500 yards, answer a question at a school in Ghana, try and decode an African puzzle, and then we got stuck at this task. In this task we had to roll a small bicycle rim with a tiny stick back and forth on a soccer field. After fighting for the heat for so long, we run into this pretty scary incident that you see in the video.

Huge thanks to everyone that has supported Team Jumba so far, you guys are the best. My dad and I are going to try our best to bounce back.
